rComments: Sid Dology is a really good professor. He is very knowledgeable about the material and helpful. There is a lot of material covered so much sure you keep up with the work and attend his lectures and you will do well

I had Professor Dolgoy for Economics and he was amazing. The course material is heavy, but if you do your readings, you should be ok. He definitely has extensive knowledge of the material and can easily address student queries. He cracks jokes too :)

I really loved this class the professor is the best I have had so far, his lectures are long but he provides several real life examples, he gives you one assignment which seems hard at first but if you have read the chapters and pay attention to his lecture you'll do fine. Mid-term and final are pretty fair. I would take another course with him.
